description:
Imagine not having access to medical care when you need it most. 

In the West-Central Africa Division, while more and more people leave their homes in search for refuge from wars and persecution, attaining medical care can be a challenge.

For this reason, Health Expos within the west-central Africa region seeks to provide physical and spiritual care for those in need. 

Find more Adventist news from around the world on adventist.news
fulltitle: Adventist Church in West Africa Helps People Physically and Spiritually
